         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">7/6/92 ¶  ¶ By this week's post, noble friend, I am sending you a small parcel of lichens that were collected during Sir Thomas Elder's Expedition in 1891, ¶  and a second small parcel will follow wit...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">92.06.07a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Jean Müller</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Conservatoire et Jarden botanique, Geneva.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">7/6/92</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Durch diese Wochen-Post, edler Freund, sende ich Ihnen eine kleine Pakete Flechten, welche während Sir Thomas Elder’s Expedition 1891 gesammelt wurden, u. ein zweites Päckchen wird mit nächster "Mail" folgen. Würden Sie so freundlich sein, </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">bald</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> die Namen zu senden, da während 1892 schon eine Liste der Expeditions Pflanzen veröffentlicht werden soll.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Herrn Finselbach brachte mir in voriger Woche Ihr Einführungs Schreiben, auch eins von dem Nestor Alph. DC. Ich habe mit diesem jungen Chemiker bereits zwei längere Unterredungen gehabt, und werde ihm an diesem Abend weitere Rathschläge ertheilen.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Sie ehrend</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">Die unnumerirten Exemplare sind </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">unica</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">7/6/92</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>By this week's post, noble friend, I am sending you a small parcel of lichens that were collected during Sir Thomas Elder's Expedition in 1891,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">Elder Scientific Exploring Expedition, 1891-2.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> and a second small parcel will follow with the next mail. Would you be so kind as to send the names <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">soon</hi>
               </seg>, as during 1892 a list of the expedition plants is to be published.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Müller supplied a report, first published as J. Müller (1892) and republished as J. Müller [given as Mueller] (1893a). M and R. Tate expected their treatment of the phanerogams and vascular cryptogams to be published in 1892, but because of a shortage of funds it was not published until 1896 (B96.14.02); see Lucas (2018), p. 816.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mr Finselbach brought me your letter of introduction last week,<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Dr W. Finselbach, aged 27, arrived in Melbourne in June 1892 aboard <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Habsburg.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> also one from the nestor Alphonse de Candolle.<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Letters not found.</p>
               </note> I have had two long conversations with this young chemist already and will give him further advice this evening.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">The unnumbered specimens are <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">unica</hi>
               </seg>.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
